{
  "texts": [
    "We filtered the discharge summaries that were of low quality, identified by either duplicated content or containing less than 40 words.",
    "We focused on MS-DRGs and consolidated all MS-DRG codes to version 34.0.",
    "Additionally, we filtered out rare DRGs with less than 2 occurrences in the cohort.",
    "F1 and AUC scores were calculated using macro-averaged or micro-averaged method as shown in the header.",
    "Notably, in a multi-class classification problem, micro-averaged F1 score is equal to top-1 prediction accuracy when labels of all classes are considered."
  ]
}